description:
&lt;p&gt;The Regional Nursing / AHP Workforce Lead will lead the successful delivery of the regional actions to support the achievement of the CNO National Nurse Manifesto 50K Commitment with a specific focus on International Recruitment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Regional Nursing /AHP Workforce Lead will be expected to have a key role working with the national and regional Chief Nurses and teams, in being the key regional link for workforce at local, system and regional level and will work closely with national NHSE/I nursing and Health Education England teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be the Regional lead for the Directorate on nursing / AHP workforce issues and the post holder must be clinically qualified i.e. as a Registered Nurse with current appropriate professional registration.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be accountable to the Chief Nurse of the North West.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be based in the North West region . Extensive travel throughout the region and nationally will be required. The post holder will also be required to attend meetings in Leeds and London.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Marie Boles&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Director of Nursing&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Cheshire &amp; Mersey&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NHS England and NHS Improvement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mobile: 07918 368368 Email: marieboles@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PA: Mandy Clark mandyclark2@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
